text: Hannes Germann (born 1 July 1956) is a Swiss politician and current member of the Swiss Council of States for the Canton of Schaffhausen. Elected to the council in 2002, he is a member of the Swiss People's Party (SVP/UDC). ==External links== * Category:1956 births Category:Living people Category:Members of the Council of States (Switzerland) Category:Presidents of the Council of States (Switzerland) Category:Swiss People's Party politicians
